data.description: Welcome to modern sophistication at its finest! The beautiful 17412 Violet Vineyard Street located in the highly coveted subdivision of Artavia provides luxury living for an affordable price. This home is LIKE NEW and barely lived in. Soaring ceilings provide a lift-type feel and plenty of room to spare. The curved staircase in the grand foyer is sure to take your breath away. Blow your guests away with the wall of windows in the family and dining rooms. The gourmet L-shaped kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinets, built-in appliances, and quartz-covered countertops make this a chef's and/or entertainer's dream! The owners retreat offers dual vanities, a luxe soaking tub, and a generously sized shower. Entertaining is a must whether you're hosting movie night in the media room or backyard BBQs on the Texas-sized covered patio. Do not miss the opportunity to call this stunning place home. Schedule your showing today!
